arts.ttl: Utrecht strike late to rescue a point at Heracles
arts.sum: Utrecht netted a 91st minute equaliser to earn a 1-1 draw against Heracles Almelo. Utrecht were the better side in the opening stages but they couldn’t turn their dominance into a lead. Sebastien Haller came close but his backheel was kept out. Heracles grew into the game and before the break, Thomas Bruns hit the […] The post Utrecht strike late to rescue a point at Heracles appeared first on Football Oranje.
